{"tid":742151,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得譚仔/三哥個湯底有浸酸宿味？","createTime":"2018-07-14T10:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T07:49:28.000Z","uid":40757,"like":15,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f154d58d305de24ef6ed3b60397d8441dbf776b6","tid":742151,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:03:25.000Z","msg":"以前食親個湯底都係叫開辣<br />\n乜味都俾辣味蓋過哂所以唔覺<br />\n<br />\n不過呢排想食得健康啲<br />\n（我知食得譚仔都唔健康得去邊，不過都係陪人食先至去，自己食野唔會揀譚仔同三哥）<br />\n所以揀食清湯/茄湯<br />\n<br />\n但個湯底冇再啲辣cum味<br />\n再加條脷敏銳少少就黎料啦<br />\n就咁食落啲米線<br />\n嗒真少少就會食到一陣好噁頂既酸宿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟係我條脷有問題定佢間野真係咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5082f3b9b2c395e03c24fb09304417b5c03924","tid":742151,"uid":179547,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"譚仔阿姐啲汗味啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4ab9ad236b3e73c1a6f18198d6db460d55506a","tid":742151,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:07:49.000Z","msg":"邊有人去譚仔唔食辣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n清湯肌肉完全無味  好似食緊老泥咁"},{"pid":"fac71e4d733778b838f746345f173adc731aa39a","tid":742151,"uid":97482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"同感，食過清湯有啲酸宿味後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，自此次次都食酸辣"},{"pid":"10323ace6637e5c5488a6d17d98f0541e8ad0b50","tid":742151,"uid":40757,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fac71e4d733778b838f746345f173adc731aa39a","tid":742151,"uid":97482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"同感，食過清湯有啲酸宿味後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，自此次次都食酸辣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:16:48.000Z","msg":"酸辣咪又係清湯加辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d93d6aca378d74ca28a7815f84d12572de5bd0c","tid":742151,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e4ab9ad236b3e73c1a6f18198d6db460d55506a","tid":742151,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:07:49.000Z","msg":"邊有人去譚仔唔食辣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n清湯肌肉完全無味  好似食緊老泥咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:17:42.000Z","msg":"譚仔 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bb832eae3c08278aecca80f61b5d044ba9140f","tid":742151,"uid":8109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:18:38.000Z","msg":"以前細個好憎食譚仔因為啲清湯陣味好惡頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係大個左食得辣叫麻辣先會食"},{"pid":"bc3d26a15befba790234b09850020bcf27495268","tid":742151,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5bb832eae3c08278aecca80f61b5d044ba9140f","tid":742151,"uid":8109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:18:38.000Z","msg":"以前細個好憎食譚仔因為啲清湯陣味好惡頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係大個左食得辣叫麻辣先會食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b8608775810281c5fe1559e196412927db1440","tid":742151,"uid":38798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:39:19.000Z","msg":"清湯真係食過一次翻唔到轉頭，以後都唔想再食譚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e18476d79ba37e5db90ef2d3098aed887ad11e","tid":742151,"uid":193540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"三哥個糊辣無得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2174d84f3abc435f865fc748c7ce01070a0df559","tid":742151,"uid":123456,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">譚姐西水